HEADWORD: Ideologist
<hw>I`de*ol"o*gist</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>One
who treats of ideas; one who theorizes or idealizes; one versed in the
science of ideas, or who advocates the doctrines of ideology.</def></p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>An ideologue.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

